<span class="postbody">The suggestions can be cast on others in your group that are of lower level than you to force them to do something.  I often make Sk's dance while in battle, is quite humours you should try it.  The Illusions from what I have seen work on yourself, or others in a group, no level restriction.  Its not much but fun spells are just fun spells.
<br />

<br />
On a side note I have found the Ratonga illusion extremely lucky and have found many rare harvests while in this illusion.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
